# 🚀 Machine Learning Journey with MATLAB: Data Analysis and Preprocessing

Welcome! This repository is created to document and share my step-by-step practical journey through **Machine Learning with MATLAB**, starting from fundamental concepts up to advanced modeling.

The success of any AI or machine learning model is directly tied to the quality of the data we feed into it. Guided by the principle of *"Garbage In, Garbage Out (GIGO)"*, this series aims to transform raw data into processable, clean, and meaningful structures.

This work marks the first step of **"Module 4: Data Analysis and Preprocessing"**, which is one of the most critical phases of our project. By integrating a real-world scenario dataset into our system, we are laying the foundation for understanding and cleaning the data.

